lenders.name: JourneyChristmasParty
lenders.loan_because:
Each year at our annual church Christmas party, attendees bid on 1 of 4 potential pre-selected loans by dropping cash in a bucket for the respective candidate.  The top two vote-getters, by dollars donated, then compete head to head in a bid-off.  To the victor belongs the spoils of last years repaid loans, plus the majority of the current years.  2nd place takes a portion of the current year.  

The Journey also contributes to Kiva loans separately outside the annual Christmas party.
